          "text": "The finding is **invalid**. The design docs explicitly state this is intentional:\n\n- `docs/plans/043_smoke_agent_files_implement.md` line 92: *\"No `skill` field — the CI workflow passes `--skill` at invocation time.\"*\n- `docs/plans/043_smoke_agent_files_spec.md` lines 44–46: *\"`dry-skill.toml` files therefore do NOT set a `skill` field — the workflow step passes `--skill` as a flag... The workflow steps must pass `--skill $(pwd)/.github/smoke-agents/skills/smoke-skill/SKILL.md` (absolute path via `$(pwd)`) to ensure correct resolution.\"*\n\nThe relative path `skills/smoke-skill/SKILL.md` would also be wrong — `resolve.Skill()` resolves relative paths against the XDG config dir, not the repo root, so it would break in CI. The `--skill` flag with an absolute path constructed at runtime is the correct mechanism.\n\n**No change needed.** The file is correct as-is.",
